findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The functions includeInAccount() and _getCurrentSupply() use loops to find and remove addresses from the _excluded list and evaluate total supply respectively, which can cause an OUT_OF_GAS exception if there is a long excluded addresses list.

findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The functions includeInAccount() and _getCurrentSupply() use loops to find and remove addresses from the _excluded list and evaluate total supply, respectively. These functions may abort with an OUT_OF_GAS exception if there is a long excluded addresses list.
